A fork of the luasyslog-1.0.0 by Nicolas Casalini.

It provides Lua 5.2 support, revamped build system and proper module
encapsulation.

Available targets, usable with "make TARGET":

* all (default): compile C module
* dist: generate luasyslog-*.tar.gz
* rock: build the Lua rock package
* rockspec: generate luasyslog-*-1.rockspeck
* install: install everything
* install-cmod: install the C module
* install-lmod: install the Lua script
* uninstall: remove all installed files
* clean: remove files generated by "make all"
* clean-rock: remove files generated by "make rock"
* distclean: remove anything but original files
